            "title": "Large-Scale Mapping of Purple Martin Pre-Migratory Roosts Using WSR-88D Weather Surveillance Radar (Mapas a Larga Escala de los Dormideros Pre-Migratorios de Progne subis Utilizando Radares WSR-88D Para el Monitoreo del Clima)",
            "creators": [
                {
