            "title": "Activity patterns of the nectar-feeding bat Leptonycteris  yerbabuenae on the Baja California Peninsula, Mexico",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "A Nayelli",
                    "lastName": "Rivera-Villanueva"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
